<p>If we cut out the 2Million+ sub 0.01 accounts *and* the  193K sub 0.1 accounts &#8211; we still have over 170,000 &#8216;owners&#8217; as described in Table 3.</p>
<p>When you say &#8216;it would appear, then, that around 75 users are actually &#8220;using&#8221; Bitcoin&#8217; &#8211; I&#8217;m going to very charitably assume you&#8217;re just having fun&#8230; but, yes there is something very wrong with the picture *you* are attempting to paint.</p>

