				<cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.bitcoiney.com/on-that-bitcoin-paper' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Bitcoin On *that* Bitcoin paper - Bitcoiney Bitcoin Website Directory</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>

		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.loper-os.org/?p=1009&amp;cpage=1#comment-3804">October 27, 2012 at 9:55 am</a></div>

		<p>[...] Loper&amp;#8217s article lays into Bitcoin with out genuinely addressing any of the other critique, as common: http://www.loper-os.org/?p=1009 [...]</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/?p=1009&#038;buffer_share=3c2a6&#038;replytocom=3804#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-3804", "3804", "respond", "1009")'>Reply</a>		</div>
